ed="T" n="0879a16"/><persName key="A013678">釋道遵</persName>，字<persName key="A013678">宗達</persName>，姓<name>張</name>氏，<placeName key="PL000000013012">吳興</placeName>人也。夙負殊<lb
ed="T" n="0879a17"/>操，潔士稱之，榮曜不足關於心，聲塵未甞<lb
ed="T" n="0879a18"/>觸其性。至<date key="j19887831989147" from-iso="+0733-01-01" to-iso="+0733-12-31">年二十</date>，詣<placeName key="PL000000011627">天竺</placeName><persName key="A013717">義威<roleName>律師</roleName></persName>受具<lb
ed="T" n="0879a19"/>戒，事<placeName key="PL000000010025">報恩寺</placeName><persName key="A013718">興<roleName>大師</roleName></persName>──首宗毘尼傳教也。後<lb
ed="T" n="0879a20"/>學天台一心三觀<ptr type="glossary" target="#g393"/>法門，欲廣寫《法華經》，置<lb
ed="T" n="0879a21"/>道場，闢經院。一之日發其心，二之日<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2159"/>規其<lb
ed="T" n="0879a22"/>趾<ptr target="#n3338"/>，作不逾序，厥功成焉，居<placeName key="PL000000010008">支硎</placeName>之福地。<date key="j20008842001238" from-iso="+0766-02-18" to-iso="+0767-02-07"><name>大<lb
ed="T" n="0879a23"/>曆</name>元年</date>，州將<persName key="A011010">韋元甫</persName>、兵部尚書<persName key="A013720">劉晏</persName>、侍御史<lb
ed="T" n="0879a24"/><persName key="A013721">王圓</persName>、<placeName key="PL000000034453">開州</placeName>刺史<persName key="A011086">陸向</persName>、殿中侍御史<persName key="A010973">陸迅</persName>、大理<lb
ed="T" n="0879a25"/>評事<persName key="A011088">張象</persName>，競誘<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2160"/>真心，共獲殊勝。乃相與飛<lb
ed="T" n="0879a26"/>表奏聞，詔書特署為<placeName key="PL000000010025">法華道場</placeName>。自<placeName key="PL000000000150">江</placeName>以東總<lb
ed="T" n="0879a27"/>一十七所，皆因<persName key="A013678">遵</persName>之首置也。舉精行大德<lb
ed="T" n="0879a28"/>二<supplied resp="sgsz">十</supplied>七人<ptr target="#n720"/>，常持此經，以報主恩。鑄<persName key="A004206">盧舍那</persName>及<lb
ed="T" n="0879a29"/><persName key="A004206">毘盧遮那</persName>像，及多寶塔<ptr type="glossary" target="#g343"/>，修淨土當生業，造<persName key="A002843">彌<pb ed="T" n="0879b" xml:id="T50.2061.0879b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0879b01"/>陀佛</persName>。復寫「天台教益乎道場」<ptr target="#n3339"/>。置常住莊二<lb
ed="T" n="0879b02"/>區。平時講《法華玄義》<ptr target="#n1171"/>、《天台止觀》<ptr target="#n1173"/>、《四分鈔文》<ptr target="#n1290"/>，臨<lb
ed="T" n="0879b03"/>壇度人，授心揚律，徒<ptr target="#n721"/>盈石室之籌<ptr type="glossary" target="#g620"/>。<date key="j19921141997410" notAfter-iso="+0756-08-15" notBefore-iso="+0742-02-14"><name>天寶</name>中</date><ptr target="#n3340"/>，<lb
ed="T" n="0879b04"/>於<placeName key="PL000000010068">靈巖道場</placeName>，行法華三昧，忽覩大明<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2161"/>上燭<lb
ed="T" n="0879b05"/>于天──我身正念，儼在光中。異日問<persName key="A001307">荊溪</persName>，<persName key="A001307">然<lb
ed="T" n="0879b06"/><roleName>師</roleName></persName>曰：「智慧光明從心流出，非精志之所致<lb
ed="T" n="0879b07"/>耶？」又於<ref type="place" target="#PL000000010008">本寺</ref>入<placeName key="PL000000010008">法華道場</placeName>，覩此身在空中<lb
ed="T" n="0879b08"/>坐。先證者知是滌垢之相<ptr target="#n3341"/>。其年春秋七十一，<lb
ed="T" n="0879b09"/>僧夏四十六，以<date key="j20076452007645" when-iso="+0784-08-23"><name>興元</name>元年七月二十九日</date>告<lb
ed="T" n="0879b10"/>終于<placeName key="PL000000010025">支硎山寺</placeName>。僧<persName key="A013722">益<roleName>公</roleName></persName>、<persName key="A013724">翰<roleName>公</roleName></persName><ptr target="#n722"/>一夜同夢大殿<lb
ed="T" n="0879b11"/>崩，果<persName key="A013678">遵</persName>入滅。門人<persName key="A013724">靈翰</persName><ptr target="#n723"/>、<persName key="A013725">法盛</persName>、<persName key="A013726">道欣</persName>、猶子<ptr type="glossary" target="#g513"/><persName key="A013727">靈源</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0879b12"/>追慕不已，樹塔旌德焉。<!-- 碑銘四庫1071-853、1341-489，全唐文4293，禪門逸書初2-91 --></p>
